*<div id="function.imap-errors" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">imap_errors</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4, PHP 5, PHP 7)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">imap_errors</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">Returns all of the IMAP errors that have occurred</span></p>   </div>  <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.imap-errors-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>   <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">    <span class="type">array</span> <span class="methodname"><strong>imap_errors</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam">void</span>    )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    Gets all of the <acronym title="Internet Message Access Protocol">IMAP</acronym> errors (if any) that have occurred    during this page request or since the error stack was reset.   </p>   <p class="para">    When <span class="function"><strong>imap_errors()</strong></span> is called, the error stack is    subsequently cleared.   </p>  </div>   <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.imap-errors-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    This function returns an array of all of the IMAP error messages    generated since the last <span class="function"><strong>imap_errors()</strong></span> call,    or the beginning of the page. Returns <strong><code>FALSE</code></strong> if no error messages are    available.    </p>  </div>   <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.imap-errors-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <p class="para">    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link imap_last_error()} - Gets the last IMAP error that occurred during this page request</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function">{@link imap_alerts()} - Returns all IMAP alert messages that have occurred</span></li>    </ul>   </p>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/ref.imap.php">IMAP 函数</a></div></div>
